x4freetext: The FN tandem Van de Graaff accelerator.
The target thickness was kept between 2 to 4 keV for
5.8 MeV protons. Target thicknesses were determined by
observing known narrow resonances and by measuring the
yield of the 6LI(p,p) reaction for which the cross
section is known.
